      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-200 Spear&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 2 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-2 body, which is a flexible mainstay anti-ship missile.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEIMPACT warhead.  It homes in on its target using command guidance from its launching ship.

